description: Demolition of existing single-storey building; erection of part 4 (16.6m high), part 11 (37m high), part 18 (58m high) and part 20 storey (64m high) building comprising 77 residential units, 2,254sq.m business floorspace (Class B1 use), 163sq.m cafe/restaurant (Class A3 use) with associated landscaping and access arrangements.
